      <a href="/research/condensed-matter/2020/12/05/computational_electron_hydro.html"> <i>Computational Electron Hydrodynamics</i></a>
      <ul>
  <li><em>Supervised by Prof. Thomas Scaffidi &amp; Prof. Nicolas Grisouard</em></li>
  <li><em>Supported by a NSERC Undergraduate Student Research Award</em></li>
</ul>
<p>
Electron hydrodynamics is an interesting field that deals with an exotic regime in which electrons can be described by hydrodynamic equations.  I implemented a computer simulation to study the flow of these viscous electrons.

</p>


